- Based on the newly issued NOTAM for the Tehran Flight Information Region (Tehran FIR), restrictions and the closure of airports in western Iran were extended until the morning of May 25, 2026.
- According to NOTAM code A1010/26, all airports in the western part of Tehran FIR are closed, with only a few specified airports allowed limited operations from sunrise to sunset.
