- All previous flight permissions were canceled, and airlines must obtain new authorization from the Civil Aviation Organization to conduct IFR passenger flights.
- The NOTAM validity is stated as Friday, May 22, 2026 at 00:16 Iran time to Monday, May 25, 2026 at 12:00 noon Iran time.
- The report states the restrictions reflect continuing security situation and military control over western Iran's airspace and that airspace had not returned to normal conditions.

